2018-05-25 Jian Wang <jian.wang@ingenic.com>

	Backup tlbinv/tlbinvf enable from branch "sourcery-201511".

	Disable tlbinv/tlbinvf ase from ASE_EVA and set membership to mips32r3.

	In order to use tlbinv/tlbinvf on xBurst2 ,set these two insn. membership
	to mips32r3 and disable ase EVA which must use -march=p5600.

	Note: The membership mips32r3 may be update future.

2018-05-22 Jian Wang <jian.wang@ingenic.com>

	Merge MXU support from branch "sourcery-201511".

	* gas/config/tc-mips.c (md_longopts): Add mmxu and mno-mxu.
	(mips_ases): Add "mxu" mips ase defined.
	(RTYPE_MXU): New macro.
	(RTYPE_MXU_CR): Likewise.
	(MIPS32_JZ_REGISTER_NAMES): Likewise.
	(reg_names): Add MIPS32_JZ_REGISTER_NAMES to reg_names.
	(args): New struct.
	(args_mxu_opts): MXU operand match.
	(mips_parse_argument_token): For mxu insn, treat user defined
	identifier as constant instead of symbol.
	(operand_reg_mask): Handle MXU operand type.
	(fpr_read_mask): mask with OP_REG_MXU.
	(fpr_write_mask): Likewise.
	(convert_reg_type): Handle OP_REG_MXU and OP_REG_MXU_CR.
	(match_fixed_int_operand): Add OP_INT_FIXED match.
	(match_operand): Handle MXU operand type.
	(mips_ip): For mxu insn, the opcode format is 'm'.
	(md_show_usage): Add options "-mmxu" and "-mno-mxu" usages.
	* opcodes/mips-opc.c (decode_mips_operand): add MXU decode operand
	'a', 'b', 'c', 'd', 'e', 'f', 'i', 'm', 'o', 'p', 'q', 'r', 'z',
	'A', 'B', 'E', 'I', 'O', 'P', 'R', 'T', 'U'.
	(MXU) : New macro.
