2018-05-21 Jian Wang <jian.wang@ingenic.com>

	Merge MXU2 support from branch "sourcery-201511".

	bfd/
	* bfd-in2.h (bfd_reloc_code_real): New enum element
	BFD_RELOC_10_PCREL_S2 for MXU2 condition branch instructions.
	* elf32-mips.c (elf_mips_howto_table_rel): New relocation type
	R_MIPS_PC10 for MXU2 condition branch instructions.
	(mips_reloc_map): New map { BFD_RELOC_10_PCREL_S2, R_MIPS_PC10 }.
	* elfxx-mips.c (mips_elf_relocation_needs_la25_stub): Handle R_MIPS_PC10
	case.
	(mips_elf_calculate_relocation): Likewise.
	(_bfd_mips_elf_check_relocs): Likewise.
	* elfcpp/mips.h (R_MIPS_PC10): New enum element R_MIPS_PC10 to 52.
	* include/opcode/mips.h (mips_reg_operand_type): New OP_REG_MXU128 and
	OP_REG_MXU128_CR.
	(ASE_MXU128): New macro.
	* include/elf/mips.h (elf_mips_reloc_type): Add R_MIPS_PC10 relocation
	number to 52.
	* gas/config/tc-mips.c (md_longopts): Add mmxu2 and mno-mxu2.
	(mips_ases): Add "mxu2" mips ase defined.
	(RTYPE_MXU128): New macro.
	(validate_mips_insn): Skip prefix charactor '='.
	(md_begin): insert MXU R2 registers name to symbol table.
	(limited_pcrel_reloc_p): Handle BFD_RELOC_10_PCREL_S2.
	(fpr_read_mask): mask with OP_REG_MXU and OP_REG_MXU128.
	(fpr_write_mask): Likewise.
	(convert_reg_type): Handle OP_REG_MXU128 and OP_REG_MXU128_CR.
	(append_insn): Handle BFD_RELOC_10_PCREL_S2.
	(md_pcrel_from): Likewise.
	(md_apply_fix): Likewise.
